Comment: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow.
Comment: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Comment: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:29.90,orig,,0,0,0,,Who's in a relationship with who? What kind of relationship?
Comment: 0,0:00:31.35,0:00:33.05,orig,,0,0,0,,Yeah right.
Comment: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:34.55,orig,,0,0,0,,Tell me! Spit it out!
Comment: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:51.35,orig,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Comment: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:56.65,orig,,0,0,0,,What the heck? What's going on? You gotta be joking.
Comment: 0,0:00:56.65,0:01:00.40,orig,,0,0,0,,When did you step into that territory?
Comment: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:04.55,orig,,0,0,0,,No way.
Comment: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:03.15,orig,,0,0,0,,Hah.
Comment: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.95,orig,,0,0,0,,That's so lame...
Comment: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:08.80,orig,,0,0,0,,Lame.
Comment: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:12.15,orig,,0,0,0,,You're so lame, Haruhiro.
Comment: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:11.60,orig,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Comment: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:16.65,orig,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah right.
Comment: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.10,orig,,0,0,0,,He did, right? You did!
Comment: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.15,orig,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Comment: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:32.70,orig,,0,0,0,,Moguzo and Ranta, I'm counting on you to each get one.
Comment: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.05,orig,,0,0,0,,Argh!
Comment: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.30,orig,,0,0,0,,And it's {\i1}Miss{\i0} Merry to you.
Comment: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:01.66,orig,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's your method.
Comment: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.10,orig,,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:30.30,orig,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Comment: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:11.95,orig,,0,0,0,,I just wanted...
Comment: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.20,orig,,0,0,0,,No, they're normal-sized!
Comment: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:58.87,orig,,0,0,0,,So was he basically telling me to take his place, and be the leader for our party?
Comment: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:21.60,orig,,0,0,0,,Haruhiro, you can do it.
Comment: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:31.70,orig,,0,0,0,,Buy yourself a helmet, even if it's just a cheap one. I'll chip in.
Comment: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:12.65,orig,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure Merry was about to say, "see you tomorrow."
Comment: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:04.90,orig,,0,0,0,,If it's about Merry, Hayashi would be a better person to ask.
Comment: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.80,orig,,0,0,0,,It had the spots of death, so people called this kobold "Death Spots."
Comment: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:11.95,orig,,0,0,0,,And I thought, this has never happened before, so why is it happening now?

Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh... just thought you two were... in a relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for jumping to conclusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.60,0:00:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you didn't have to come so early just to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:24.50,Alt,,0,0,0,,Relationship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about being in a relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:29.40,fix,,0,0,0,,Who with whom in what kind of relationship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:30.15,Alt,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.35,0:00:33.05,fix,,0,0,0,,Like hell it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:34.55,fix,,0,0,0,,Tell me! Got it?! Spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Shihoru's trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:40.30,Alt,,0,0,0,,What kind of situation would make her jump to conclusions?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, it's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:43.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru-kun was just hugging me really tightly, and Shihoru saw us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:51.35,fix_it,,0,0,0,,Oh boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.35,0:00:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:55.27,fix,,0,0,0,,What the heck! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.27,0:00:56.65,fix,,0,0,0,,For real?! Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.65,0:01:00.40,fix,,0,0,0,,Haruhiro, when did you step into that territory?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:01.55,Alt,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.55,0:01:03.35,Alt,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it was a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:04.55,fix,,0,0,0,,No way that's the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.55,0:01:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You were definitely trying to do something there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huuuh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Haru-kun... was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Tell me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't cut out the details!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're very important, you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:19.10,Alt,,0,0,0,,Aaaah! Ah, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:28.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating a yesterday filled with scrapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:33.25,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We clear the path to a hopeful tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:48.35,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I wonder what remains
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:51.55,op/ed,,0,0,0,,in both these tiny hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:57.90,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The voice I raised upwards scattered into the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:02:01.20,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The reality I've gamed is hazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:04.30,op/ed,,0,0,0,,and even if I can't see ahead of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:07.60,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I can keep moving forward on this long road
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:11.70,op/ed,,0,0,0,,if I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:17.95,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Connecting a bond covered in dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:24.30,op/ed,,0,0,0,,We join back to back in the past and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:30.75,op/ed,,0,0,0,,Repeating an answer full of mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:38.75,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will reach out my hands to seek the light, again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:03.15,fix,,0,0,0,,Tch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.95,fix,,0,0,0,,That's so boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.65,0:03:08.80,fix,,0,0,0,,Boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:12.15,fix,,0,0,0,,You're a boring guy, Haruhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see, me and Shihoru are going\Nto try to be nicer to Merry-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It would be nice if she would just heal us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! Not with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She has no intention of doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we can't immediately treat her as part of our group,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but if we always think of her as an outsider, she'll\Nnever have a chance to become part of our group.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Merry-chan hasn't been friendly with us, but me\Nand Shihoru haven't exactly been friendly to her either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That might be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She actually might be a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We added her to our party,\Nso doesn't that make her a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, having her is better than having no Priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, does that mean... maybe she'll fawn over me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not half bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:16.65,fix,,0,0,0,,O-Obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...no way she would... fawn over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Moguzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Moguzo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just make a comeback at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.05,fix,,0,0,0,,Hey! For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,See what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:46.70,Italics,,0,0,0,,She gives me that look when I'm just greeting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:04:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So Merry-chan, what did you eat for breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How long have you been a Volunteer Soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any snacks you like to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I like—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:32.75,fix,,0,0,0,,Moguzo. Ranta. I'm counting on you to each get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yume and I will get the third.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shihoru and Merry will back us up from the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Marque, Em, Parc!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pull back from such a weak attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a Warrior?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, she's so stuck up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not even helping!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohm, Rel, Ect, Well, Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:45.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,I can tell I hit a critical spot by the resistance I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take my Vice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Our teamwork wasn't great, but what a huge victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I defeated it in one fell swoop, so it was all thanks to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But man, my hand hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry, heal it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,O light, return to Lumiaris' divine protection. Cure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:31.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}will{\i0} heal us, as long as it's after the fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough for Moguzo, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nu-uh. Look at all this bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting to clot up, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you spit on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.35,fix,,0,0,0,,Also, don't be so familiar with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're this close from me losing my temper at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.66,fix,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's your method?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry, you have a set way in how you work as a healer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.15,fix,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was just thinking that\Nthere are different types of Priests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato was a perfectionist...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...so he couldn't sit still until we were in the best condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:30.30,fix,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Will you... tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a Thief, so I don't know much about Priests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's perfectly fine if you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't pry into your personal life or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:09:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it'd be nice to all talk about\Nour roles and responsibilities in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like how I work, just say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:13.55,Alt,,0,0,0,,Then what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:17.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,Someone tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:22.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,...the way to properly communicate with Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon now, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is so full of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I just get juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Merry-chan doesn't react\Nthe same way as most people do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But that did hurt a little just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, we didn't say anything either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she was thinking, "they probably won't say 'hi,'"\Nand was preparing herself mentally for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to be so considerate of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exactly why girls hate you, Ranta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing a flat-chested girl has the right to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:40.17,Alt,,0,0,0,,Flat-chest! Flat-chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.85,Alt,,0,0,0,,Flat-chest! Flat-chest! Flat-chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.20,Alt,,0,0,0,,They're not flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:46.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,Yume definitely doesn't seem that small...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.05,Alt,,0,0,0,,My breas—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:45.60,Alt,,0,0,0,,What are you making me say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's talking to Merry-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Shinohara-san from Orion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That clan's famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And isn't Shinohara the master of Orion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:47.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,Manato... said he's entrust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.00,fix_it,,0,0,0,,So, basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:52.20,fix_it,,0,0,0,,Manatto was telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.20,fix_it,,0,0,0,,...that I have to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:58.40,fix_it,,0,0,0,,In other words... become a party leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:03.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,Someone has to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,But truthfully, I don't want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:09.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,I don't want to bear that burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:21.70,fix,,0,0,0,,You can do it... Haruhiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Manato...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...Haruhiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...how our party... will turn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:39.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,Moguzo is more cautious than usual,\Nbecause he has no helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:44.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,If he had a helmet, he wouldn't die from a blow to the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:51.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'm a Thief, so I usually attack from behind,\Nbut that's not an option for Moguzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.80,Alt,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:03.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,Our roles are different, so I never\Nunderstood Moguzo's fighting style.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:06.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,No, that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.45,Italics,,0,0,0,,I never tried to observe his fighting style in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:13.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,That's also unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,I never thought Merry to be the type to pray over the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:21.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,But, I don't actually know anything about Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,I never asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Moguzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll chip in, so buy yourself a helmet,\Neven if it's just a cheap one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No, you shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to chip in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's everyone's loss if you don't have proper equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you get proper armor,\Nyou'd be able to fight all out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's for my own good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, that's a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll contribute some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all look for a cute helmet together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I want to help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not just standing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:23.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,Merry said her staff is just for show, but that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:26.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,She's learned skills for her staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:30.10,Italics,,0,0,0,,She just doesn't want to fight on the front lines,\Nbut she still protected Shihoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Merry, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.60,Italics,,0,0,0,,She's scary every single time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,Aren't we friends in the same party?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:04.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,Isn't it better to be liked than hated?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,I'd like to say that to her, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:13.25,Italics,,0,0,0,,If I say anything personal, she'll probably leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's not that important...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you wanna... grab a bite with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Why are you being so formal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,See you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, she's a real nasty one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a little different today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Merry-chan was kinda cute today, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:09.00,fix_it,,0,0,0,,"See you tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:12.75,fix_it,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure Merry was about to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:16.55,Italics,,0,0,0,,That's what I decided to think today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I want to go ask Shinohara-san from Orion something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you all come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking about Merry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You were talking to her yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you tell us about Merry?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.85,0:17:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think she would tell us anything if we asked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:04.95,fix,,0,0,0,,Then... rather than me, Hayashi\Nwould be a better person to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayashi used to be in Merry's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry and I were friends from when we were\NTrainee Volunteer Soldiers, just like you all are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Michiki and I were Warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutsumi was our Mage, Ogu was\Nour Thief, and Merry was our Priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Our party was one that had a smooth start.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We bought our badges after about ten days,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and we weren't exposed to real danger until we\Nbegan our hunt for a kobold in the Cyrene Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, we took how easy it was for granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:19:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we didn't realize how much\Nof a burden we were putting on Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She was always bright, cheerful, and smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So much that our party was never gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She would heal us right away, even if it was just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And if Mutsumi or Ogu were in trouble, she would\Nhelp them right away, so of course we had it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry was doing enough for three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The more battles we fought, the more our confidence grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't afraid of anything back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But the difference between victory and defeat is paper-thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't realize this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...and were arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But Merry always prevented the thing\Nthat could make us fall into utter defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Other parties had also been trying to seize\NCyrene Mine, and we didn't want to lose to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Deeper and deeper we went.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the fifth layer down, we met it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A giant, black and white-spotted kobold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A great number of Volunteer Soldiers had died by its hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,People called this kobold "Death Spots."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We had the chance to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret that more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The kobold hit me, and I fell unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came to, Ogu and Mutsumi were dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:21:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Michiki, who was covered in wounds,\Nwas desperately trying to hold back Death Spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Over and over, I shouted to Merry to go and heal Michiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:09.10,fix,,0,0,0,,This has never happened before...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:10.75,fix,,0,0,0,,...so why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.00,fix,,0,0,0,,...why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Hayashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've used up all my magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, we lost three of our members.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's when she stopped smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.50,0:21:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"I've let three of my precious comrades... friends... die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no right to be a healer..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...is probably what she was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:23.20,op/ed,,0,0,0,,When I try touching
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.30,0:22:29.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,the dry air after a rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.55,0:22:36.10,op/ed,,0,0,0,,like a sprouting flower,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:42.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,fragments of memories overflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:55.05,op/ed,,0,0,0,,The warmth you gave this hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:23:03.85,op/ed,,0,0,0,,led me to a future I can treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:06.62,op/ed,,0,0,0,,always.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.62,0:23:13.80,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I chased your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.80,0:23:19.45,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I wonder when you became so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.45,0:23:26.40,op/ed,,0,0,0,,I will probably find what I searched the vast world for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:33.95,op/ed,,0,0,0,,at the end of this journey.
